author: Ashley Walls
title: Monday’s prep volleyball results
text: Monday’s prep volleyball results Originally published October 12, 2015 at 10:08 pm Jadyn Mullen posted a double-double with 51 assists and 22 digs at Emerald Ridge defeated Graham Kapowsin at home. By Ashley Walls Garfield 3, West Seattle 0 Deahna Kraft had 20 kills and Alina Zatzick led the offense with 27 assists in Garfield’s sweep of West Seattle in a Metro League match. Renita Gray added seven kills and four aces for the Bulldogs and Ginny Barnes had 14 digs. Emerald Ridge 3, Graham Kapowsin 2 Jadyn Mullen racked up 51 assists and 22 digs and Makenna Smith recorded 24 kills and 10 digs for the Jaguars as Emerald Ridge defeated Graham Kapowsin in five sets. Allie Bauer added 31 digs. For the Eagles, Peyton Foster posted a double-double performance with 10 kills and 15 digs, Jordan Keane had 46 assists, and Hannah Barbour added 32 digs.
